sec.p:
We will use following sets of colors in our construction of an instance of NLCP:
(1) S = {σ[i, j] : 1 ≤ i 6= j ≤ k}
(2) S0 = {σ0[i, j] : 1 ≤ i 6= j ≤ k}
(3) T = {τi[r, s] : 1 ≤ i ≤ k, 1 ≤ r < s ≤ k, r 6= i, s 6= i}
(4) T 0 = {τi0[r, s] : 1 ≤ i ≤ k, 1 ≤ r < s ≤ k, r 6= i, s 6= i}
(5) E = { [i, j] : 1 ≤ i < j ≤ k}
(6) E 0 = { 0[i, j] : 1 ≤ i < j ≤ k}
